///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
/**
 * @file MessageParser.dox
 * @brief Examples using the MessageParser class from the MIDILAR MIDI Core module.
 */
///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
/**
 * @addtogroup MIDILAR_Examples_MessageParser
 * @brief Practical examples showcasing MIDI message parsing using the MessageParser class.
 *
 * This group includes curated examples demonstrating how to use the `MessageParser` class
 * to interpret raw MIDI byte streams and route them to specific callback handlers.
 *
 * Each example explores a different use case for parsing and handling MIDI messages,
 * such as real-time byte streaming, structured message simulation, or callback routing.
 * These examples are intended to clarify the usage of the parser in both embedded
 * and desktop environments.
 *
 */
///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
/**
 * @defgroup MIDILAR_Examples_MessageParser_StandaloneCallbacks Standalone Callback Example
 * @ingroup MIDILAR_Examples_MessageParser
 * @brief Demonstrates how to bind simple standalone functions to the MessageParser.
 */
///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
/**
 * @defgroup MIDILAR_Examples_MessageParser_InstanceCallbacks Instance Callback Example
 * @ingroup MIDILAR_Examples_MessageParser
 * @brief Demonstrates how to bind member functions of a class to the MessageParser.
 */
///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
/**
 * @defgroup MIDILAR_Examples_MessageParser_ParsingSim Simulated Parsing Example
 * @ingroup MIDILAR_Examples_MessageParser
 * @brief Feeds a stream of valid and invalid MIDI data to the parser to test routing and robustness.
 */
///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
/**
 * @defgroup MIDILAR_Examples_MessageParser_ParsingRT Real-Time Parsing Example
 * @ingroup MIDILAR_Examples_MessageParser
 * @brief Demonstrates real-time, byte-by-byte parsing using serial or MIDI stream input.
 */
